  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">HELP THE FLOOD AFFECTEES OF SINDH, PAKISTAN</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Floods are one of the most common hazards in Pakistan. FLOOD 2020 hits Pakistan putting people of Pakistan in crisis thrice in a year. SINDH province is badly affected as houses are damaged,  livestock and crops flashed away and people are on roads. This project intends to help 200 poorest of the poor families of CALAMITY affected villages of District DADU and District Sanghar. People are in dire need of drinking water, food, Utensils, winterization kits, hygiene items, tents and livestock.</narrative>
  </description>
